            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%8A%A4%E8%82%A41%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%97%E8%84%B8%E8%87%B4%E6%BB%A1%E8%84%B8%E7%BB%93%E7%97%82%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%BA%E6%8A%A4%E8%82%A41%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%97%E8%84%B8%E8%87%B4%E6%BB%A1%E8%84%B8%E7%BB%93%E7%97%82%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女子为护肤1个月不洗脸致满脸结痂#</span></a>】近日，深圳的小何（化名）偶然刷到这样的一则视频：30天不洗脸，你会发现皮肤状态越来越好，于是决定试试1个月不洗脸、不涂护肤品。结果一个月后，她的脸上结满了黄棕色的痂。深圳市第三人民医院医生表示，这是长期不清洁皮肤导致的皮肤垢着病。经过清洁和修复皮肤屏障，1周后，小何皮肤状态好转。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[摊手]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_tanshou-fa05d4eacf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5011125889073165" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">巨浪视频的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/008s5fZbly1hno8zbdd86j30u01404n1.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/G5nCztnHlx08de8TLarC010412008Ob00E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1710381303&amp;ssig=rmPLUQDjGW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/IIla4QYblx08de8SRWxy010412005j5D0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1710381303&amp;ssig=%2B%2BeCgoC71Z&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/TQO5HL7Ulx08de8SGiHS010412002XE10E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=4ub7gI97adQ&amp;Expires=1710381303&amp;ssig=ei5EwPokRa&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5011125889073165" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
